# {{ .Name }}

Serverless application built with Forge.

## Getting Started

```bash
# Deploy all stacks
forge deploy

# Deploy specific stack
forge deploy <stack-name>

# Destroy infrastructure
forge destroy
```

## Project Structure

```
.
├── forge.hcl           # Project configuration
└── <stack-name>/       # Individual Lambda functions
    ├── stack.forge.hcl # Stack configuration
    ├── main.tf         # Terraform configuration
    └── ...             # Function code
```

## Commands

- `forge deploy` - Build and deploy stacks
- `forge destroy` - Destroy all infrastructure
- `forge new <name>` - Create a new stack
